        {
            "title": "聯合利華接近與味好美達成協議 打造600億美元食品巨頭——華爾街日報",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UbWk.IxVhORjrFHxRfsMaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEE8B0BG_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯合利華\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯合利華;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯合利華\">聯合利華</a>(LON:ULVR)正就其食品業務與香料製造商味好美(NYSE:MKC)的合併進行深入談判,該交易將創建一家價值600億美元的新巨頭。據《華爾街日報》援引知情人士報導,該交易包含債務,最早可能於週二宣布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家好樂門蛋黃醬製造商的董事會於週一下午召開會議,審查這項待定交易的具體細節。這項現金加股票交易的時機可能與味好美最新季度業績公布同步,但消息人士提醒稱,計劃仍可能延後。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-70400263-52b4-312d-b10f-02c609749b86-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span>聯合利華</span></span>的這一重大戰略轉變延續了消費品集團精簡全球業務部門的更廣泛趨勢。此舉將使這家總部位於英國的聯合利華主要專注於其美容、個人護理和家居產品部門。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預計聯合利華股東在交易完成後將擁有新成立食品業務約三分之二的股權。據報導,該交易包含約160億美元的現金部分,以滿足相關各方的要求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該交易預計將採用反向莫里斯信託結構,以最大化潛在稅收優惠。聯合利華目前市值超過1,300億美元,旗下擁有家樂牌湯料等標誌性品牌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">味好美市值略高於140億美元,以其標誌性的紅蓋香料瓶而聞名。其產品組合包括法式黃芥末醬、Old Bay調味料和Cholula辣醬等家喻戶曉的品牌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報導發布後,味好美股價在盤後交易中上漲1.5%,顯示投資者對該交易充滿信心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
